high_descs: Turn right and walk over to the fridge, then turn right and across the room to the wooden table.
Pick up the large metal pot off of the wooden table.
Walk over to the fridge that is behind you.
Open the fridge and put the large metal pot inside then close the door, after a couple seconds open the fridge and take the pot back out, then close the fridge.
Turn right and walk over to the wall, then turn right and walk up to the wooden table.
Put the chilled metal pot on the wooden table.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled metal pot on the wooden table.

high_descs: Turn around, take a left towards the fridge and walk to the large wooden table on the right.
Pick up the silver pot to the right of the toaster on the table.
Turn around and walk to the black fridge ahead.
Put the pot inside the fridge on the top shelf, chill it, remove it and close the doors.
Turn around and walk to the large wooden table.
Put the chilled pot behind the head of lettuce in the middle of the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled pot on a table.

high_descs: Turn around and veer left to the wooden table in the left corner of the room.
Pick up the pot on the table.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Place the pot on the top right shelf of the fridge. Close the door, wait a moment, and take it out again.
Turn around and walk to the table.
Place the pot on the table to the right of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled pot on a table.
